title: 01/06/21 - HOUR 2 - Doug Dieken
itunes:title: 01/06/21 - HOUR 2 - Doug Dieken
description:
Dan discusses the latest on Ohio State and Devonta Smith's Heisman award ahead of Monday's college football's title game. Former NFL star and radio color analyst Doug Dieken joins the show to discuss the Cleveland Browns.
